# âš™ï¸ Setup & Execution

Prerequisites

âœ… Java 11+ (or Java 21, as configured in pom.xml)

âœ… Maven 3.8+

âœ… Chrome/Firefox (for Selenium WebDriver)

âœ… Jenkins (for CI/CD)

## 1ï¸âƒ£ Running Locally
### Install dependencies
`mvn clean install`
### Run tests (with TestNG)
`mvn test`
### Generate Allure report
`allure serve allure-results`

## 2ï¸âƒ£ Running in Jenkins
Create a new Jenkins job (Freestyle or Pipeline).

## Set up Git repo:
Repository URL: https://github.com/fahim150283/AutomationWithJenkins.git

Branch: master
## Add build step:
`mvn clean test`

## Add Post-build Action: 
Publish Allure Report (allure-results/)

